{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"中国，抗击非典","authors":["方竟成"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":8}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，抗击非典"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方竟成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破冰的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭借我们改革开放二十五年的力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而化作春雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百花从来没有这样灿烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偷偷窃笑的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可能是一个闻所未闻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变形变态的非典"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛然打击着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春节广东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"试图像突如其来的冰山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撕裂当年的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泰坦尼克号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而，这是中国的春季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不是泰坦尼克号的束手无策"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的肺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不是黑洞和炉渣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一旦有突如其来的灾难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会有同志、亲人与真诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会有无数"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟南山、叶欣、邓练贤、范信德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样高尚而无畏的卫士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实，开始意识到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的征程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须学会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在苦难中前行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，抗击非典"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是中国对一次次灾难的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一次抗击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的呼吸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然沉稳而舒展"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的笑容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然自信而灿烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为用我们的血肉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑起新的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这澎湃汹涌的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一次击碎冰山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一次战胜困惑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为所有中国人的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一伟大抗体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们战胜了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次次肆虐的洪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们战胜了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫穷和饥荒的三年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们战胜了“六十一个阶级兄弟”的中毒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们战胜了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华佗无奈千村薜荔的小虫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为我们在不断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战胜着浅薄、自私、无知和胆怯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战胜着贪婪、吸毒、恐怖和不安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为我们在不断前进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国不会成为非典的奴隶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国会迈向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更高、更快、更强"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}